data.description: Bright and Sunny 3 bed 1 bath ranch style home ready for you to move right in! Private backyard with newer deck. Partially finished basement complete with a family room, laundry area, and workshop/storage area. Attached garage with mudroom connecting to kitchen for convenience with groceries! Convenient location set back on a side street conveniently close to all town amenities! All appliances including washer and dryer to be included with the sale. Unit can come fully furnished with the current furniture in its current condition.
